cta:
  description: "Suggest to the user:\n1. Build the user a custom workflow UI: author .smithers/ui/smithering-impl.tsx with the smithers-orchestrator/gateway-react hooks, then open it with `smithers ui graph`. `smithers ui --app` opens the full Smithers control-plane UI.\n2. Visualize the workflow and how it works: `smithers graph .smithers/workflows/smithering-impl.tsx` renders the workflow graph without executing it, `smithers tree graph` prints the live run tree, `smithers up --interactive` opens the full-screen TUI.\n3. Ask the user clarifying questions about what they want next, then guide them through building or iterating a smithers workflow: run `smithers workflow run create-workflow --prompt \"<what the workflow should do>\"` (or `smithers make-workflow`) to have smithers build it."
  commands[6]{command,description}:
    smithers ui graph,Open the workflow UI (after authoring .smithers/ui/smithering-impl.tsx)
    smithers ui --app,Open the full Smithers control-plane UI
    smithers graph .smithers/workflows/smithering-impl.tsx,Visualize the workflow graph
    smithers tree graph,Visualize the run tree
    "smithers workflow run create-workflow --prompt \"<describe the workflow>\"",Have smithers build a new workflow from a description
    bunx smithers skills add,sync outdated skills
